BRIEF-Alliance Select Foods International's Board Approves Changing Unit's Core Business

Stock Markets 43 minutes ago (Oct 21, 2019 09:40)

BRIEF-Alliance Select Foods International's Board Approves Changing Unit's Core Business Oct 21 (Reuters) - Alliance Select Foods International Inc

:

* BOARD APPROVES CHANGING PT INTERNATIONAL ALLIANCE FOOD

INDONESIA'S CORE BUSINESS OPERATIONS TO EXPORT TRADING

* PT IAFI TO RELOCATE OPERATIONS TO JAKARTA, DECIDED TO

DISPOSE

FIXED ASSETS IN BITUNG CITY

* BOARD APPROVED SALE OF PT IAFI'S LAND & BUILDINGS TO PT

MULTI

NABATI SULAWESI, UNIT OF WILMAR INTERNATIONAL
